			"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg",
			"system":{
				"description":{
					"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>A strange, many-faceted gem in the center of the chamber suddenly emits blasts of blinding light.</i></p><p><b>Trap:</b> A glittering diamond set in a Huge stone statue flashes with light. When a creature draws too close, the light intensifies to scorch the infidel.</p>",
